<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>《眼儿媚》</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>———词林正韵</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong> 文/宽哥</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">幻变霓灯酒千樽，玉液醉佳人。繁弦急管，舞狂意乱，夜半销魂。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">人生长恨春宵短，梦醒枕衾痕。昔时己逝，明朝未卜，莫负良辰。</p>
