http://www.sohu.com/a/430663310_100115135	38579
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20201109/8326442e65ef4f6b8e8fa9f067142449.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>初冬种菊有感</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>文/小隐</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">秋去冬闲菊正黄，小园初种半苔荒。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">梅花香雪寒迟到，欲借篱东作故乡。</p>
