<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>水调歌头·好友邀相聚</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>文/张立标</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">好友邀相聚，追忆旧时空。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">珍馐佳酿，畅怀幽叙故情浓。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">已是霜须鬓雪，难却一觞一咏，三盏颇从容。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">余生养真趣，难得老来疯。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>游山水，戏江月，宿乌篷。</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>武陵花盛，更喜陶菊傲秋风。</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>莫叹冯唐易老，白首丹心可鉴，方显大英雄。</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>且喜闲身健，杖履过江东。</strong></p>
