➜广西诗人陈熠明：原来秋里梦藏春
http://www.sohu.com/a/430666913_100115135	39590
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20201109/4ef678d731bf4ba88fdb896707ede679.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>原来秋里梦藏春</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>(一)</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>七绝·原来秋里梦藏春</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>诗文作者·陈熠明</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">相思树上花撩眼，翠色藤萝碧玉魂。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">不见繁花嫣影在，原来秋里梦藏春。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>(二)</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>七绝·秋风锁院话真情</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>诗文作者·陈熠明</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">何时有梦见兰亭，静好时光问柳青。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">乱眼藤缠花影在，秋风锁院话真情。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>(三)</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>七绝·藤萝碧玉隐风流</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>诗文作者·陈熠明</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">翠色青华芳雨露，藤萝碧玉隐风流。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">红蝶醉意心留梦，满目春花院里秋。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20201109/36fa0fdfac0f4908a1e9b7b40d42ba26.png" max-width="600" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
<div class="lookall-shadow"></div>
<section class="lookall">
<a href="javascript:;" class="show-all" id="showMore">
<em>展开全文</em>
</a>
</section>
</div>
<div class="hidden-content control-hide">
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>(四)</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>七绝·往事青梅另有春</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>诗文作者·陈熠明</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">日暮窗前落影昏，娇藤满院翠销魂。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">相思树上风流话，往事青梅另有春。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>(五)</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>七绝·泪眼窗前留故事</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>诗文作者·陈熠明</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">南墙碧玉芳藤蔓，绚丽云花正始开。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">泪眼窗前留故事，春风隐梦入秋怀。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>(六)</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>七绝·芳藤热恋正初秋</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>诗文作者·陈熠明</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">时光静好玉兰修，不舍春华付水流。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">等你前缘花有梦，芳藤热恋正初秋。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20201109/145f44e6c94f433f9c4428e39cc0d8bc.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>(七)</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>七绝·秋风院上花留影</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>诗文作者·陈熠明</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">乱眼蝴蝶枝海落，云霞烂漫紫烟生。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">秋风院上花留影，绑定前缘碧玉藤。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>(八)</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>七绝·红蝶对影话青兰</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>诗文作者·陈熠明</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">碧玉流连伴紫丹，红蝶对影话青兰。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">前尘你是藤缠树，注定今生恋我攀。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>(九)</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>七绝·丹心碧玉话秋风</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>诗文作者·陈熠明</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">留言转世芳菲远，等你青华梦里逢。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">热恋藤缠花影伴，丹心碧玉话秋风。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20201109/8f9b46db4e154190979fc76014f7f4c3.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>(十)</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>七绝·芳藤蔓上我秋风</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>诗文作者·陈熠明</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">流连碧玉水烟生，酒醉红蝶梦海逢。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">等远轮回花又是，芳藤蔓上我秋风。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>(十一)</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>七绝·不为高攀比艳芳</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>诗文作者·陈熠明</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">院上寒门心锁梦，藏身世外隐飞扬。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">虚心只向青藤蔓，不为高攀比艳芳。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>(十二)</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>七绝·梦海青藤玉品芳</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>诗文作者·陈熠明</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">翠色绫罗幻紫光，缠绵碧树韵娇藏。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">随缘静好花常艳，梦海青藤玉品芳。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20201109/5c7f06a9d22445fc8da8a8137528fffd.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p>▲<strong>【作者简介】：</strong>陈熠明，笔名心灵诗幻，男，1976年生，广西平果市人。爱好文学创作，曾有诗歌作品发布于多家报刊杂志和网络。时任星连文学社副社长。职业于中医，热衷于传统文化传播。诗是文笔与文笔的向往，诗是朋友与朋友的交心。诗是千难和万险的将来，诗是岁月与年华的渴望。诗是春夏和秋冬的风景，诗是父亲和母亲的嘱咐，诗是父亲和母亲的叮咛。诗是渡船与碧波的远航，诗是生命与大海的彼岸。</p>
